# Purity Rules for domain/tests/**
#
# All functions in this directory must be PURE:
# - Deterministic: same inputs â†’ same outputs
# - Side-effect free: no I/O, no logging, no global state
# - Time-independent: no Date.now(), new Date() without arguments
#
# FORBIDDEN patterns in *.ts files (excluding *.test.ts):
# - Date.now()
# - new Date() without arguments
# - Math.random()
# - localStorage, sessionStorage
# - window, document, navigator
# - console.log, console.warn, console.error
# - fetch, XMLHttpRequest
# - setTimeout, setInterval
# - process.env (use dependency injection)
#
# If a function needs current time, pass `now: Date` as a parameter.
# If a function needs random values, pass `random: () => number` as a parameter.
